  "title": "Community Nurse",
  "description": "<p>Staff Nurse to perform home-based nursing procedures including IV infusion, wound care, urinary catherization and change, NGT insertions, blood taking, IDC change and flusing, fleet procedure, manual evacuation, suctioning with machine etc.</p>\n<p>Able to operate and calibrate equipment such Oxygen Concentrator, Compat Ella Pump, Suction Machine, Nebulizer, Infusion Pump, Syringe Pump etc.</p>\n<p>Able to use simple CRM software (PLATO Medical) to compute invoice and bill patients.</p>\n<p>Having own vehicle with qualified driving licence is an advantage.</p>",
