    "description": "<h2>CareHome Nursing Pte Ltd&nbsp;</h2>\n<p>CareHome was founded 2019 base in Singapore. We aim to provide complete and efficient one-stop home health care for the clients. The Company is to provide best Home Health Care with available community medical resources. Our vision is to provide best satisfying home health care for all our clients. We treat our clients with our knowledge and attitude. We believe in not only treating numbers, but also individual well-beings. At end of the day, brightening our patient’s living at home, also give the family member peace of mind. &nbsp;&nbsp;We do provide Manpower supply services to multiple healthcare orgnizations too from 2020.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
